    Keychron K2 V2 Wireless Mechanical Keyboard

    Modern keyboards are great — slim, responsive, and generally reliable (Butterfly mechanism, we're looking at you). Yet many yearn for the days of physical switches and the satisfying clack that comes with it. The Keychron K2 version 2.0 Wireless Mechanical Keyboard offers that, with modern convenience and classic style, and the stability and durability of its aluminum chassis. It can be used via Bluetooth or traditional USB hard-wire, arrives with 3 specific keycaps for Mac and Windows, and has RGB backlighting to match your (likely) work from home setup. If you're more mobile, it also works great with iPads and tablets. This is the "brown switch" key model sitting atop an aluminum chassis, offering tactile and quite key response that's best suited for WFH office use or occasional gaming on the side.

    Buy From Uncrate Supply

    The Nue Co. Skin Filter

    Moisturizers, masks, and serums can enhance the skin from the outside. The Nue Co. Skin Filter improves luminosity, pigmentation, blemishes, and elasticity from within. Made with a blend of Vitamin C, Zinc, Champagne Grape Seed, and Melon, the daily supplement boosts dull, uneven skin by treating collagen degradation, melanin overproduction, and impaired microcirculation. The result is a better complexion in as little as 60 days.
